{"tid":1756011,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中大罔顧職員人命?","createTime":"2019-11-26T00:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T08:52:54.000Z","uid":50054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78b3e7990630af1a2a047ad4bda65989fbc59606","tid":1756011,"uid":50054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:43:48.000Z","msg":"同朋友傾開發現原來中大琴日已經叫哂人返工<br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK見到四五日前有人入過去都仲話係一陣惡臭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/matthew.l.wong.1/posts/10220815625844004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmatthew.l.wong.1%2Fposts%2F10220815625844004&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV00BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=c20e2d09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/matthew.l.wong.1/posts/10220815625844004</a><br />\n<br />\n中大個聲明話驗緊二噁英, 但要兩星期先公佈結果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cpr.cuhk.edu.hk/tc/press_detail.php?1=1&amp;id=3178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cpr.cuhk.edu.hk%2Ftc%2Fpress_detail.php%3F1%3D1%26id%3D3178&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV00BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=99f7cb7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cpr.cuhk.edu.hk/tc/press_detail.php?1=1&amp;id=3178</a><br />\n<br />\n唔係應該驗完確實無野先叫人返去咩, 仲要等兩個星期咁耐, 係有事既都中哂毒啦, 仲驗黎把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d2e165de32775a1049de77f3fdc08cb4f7a524","tid":1756011,"uid":50054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:06:49.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b967a51f47f4b49d815a5bfcd32ead3292cb80b0","tid":1756011,"uid":63927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\